de.unipassau.im.ontoint.model
Class WrappedOWLEntity

java.lang.Object
  de.unipassau.im.ontoint.model.WrappedOWLEntity

public final class WrappedOWLEntity
extends java.lang.Object

Not really a wrapper but a data holding class that represents the basic information from the original OWL API OWLEntity. Because this entity will be serialized together with the TemplateProposalTrie, it is more practically to just save any necessary information.

Author:
Philipp Nolte
